{
  "texts": [
    "However, designers used and appropriated features of Multi-modal condition in innovative and unexpected ways.",
    "Some designers input extremely long image prompts (P9, P12).",
    "P9 once tuned an image with 5 other images and she \"couldn't really imagine an image based on all of that\".",
    "P12 used a lengthy compound input with multiple modalities and quickly switched between base modalities.",
    "Additionally, P12 explored color as \"a theme\" rather than a descriptor in her design."
  ]
}